body:
Fixed this by adding a `tauri.linux.conf.json` with this in (`icons/icon.icns` is removed):

```json
{
  "tauri": {
    "bundle": {
      "identifier": "com.daniel-knights.note-boi",
      "icon": [
        "icons/32x32.png",
        "icons/128x128.png",
        "icons/128x128@2x.png",
        "icons/icon.ico"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

No idea if this is the right approach, though.
